---
title: Ginger Jumbo Shrimp and Rice with Mixed Veggies and Candied Walnuts
description: Get ready for a new twist on an Asian classic. Our version of honey-walnut shrimp features succulent jumbo shrimp and a creamy ginger sauce, along with crunchy, candied walnuts and a hearty blend of broccoli, cabbage and carrots.
